quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,28,"How can you disbelieve in Allâh? seeing that you were dead and He gave you life. Then He will give you death, then again will bring you to life (on the Day of Resurrection) and then unto Him you will return (See V.40:11)"
  2,29,"He it is Who created for you all that is on earth. Then He rose over (Istawâ) towards the heaven and made them seven heavens and He is the All-Knower of everything."
  2,30,"And (remember) when your Lord said to the angels: "